{"tid":2428073,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"一個Cathie Wood信徒感言","createTime":"2021-03-01T09:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T12:55:35.000Z","uid":73956,"like":103,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf7dd63514f24cafdc722abe02017ce1b878153","tid":2428073,"uid":73956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:42:50.000Z","msg":"我係一個平凡人。<br />\n<br />\n上年開始認識Arkk同Cathie，<br />\n一路買貨、揸貨到宜家。<br />\n經歷過Arkk升跌，過程中充滿上升興奮，<br />\n下跌風雨衝撃，記得第一次Arkk下跌時候有動搖過，不過最後堅持住，因為Cathie係一個偉大專業者，<br />\n佢比我明智，所以我比佢一試，<br />\n結果挨過、長升。<br />\n我挨過每一次下跌衝撃，都係成長，加大我對Cathie信心。時間越耐，我對Cathie信心越大，<br />\n時間證明一切。<br />\n<br />\n上星期Arkk跌得比平時多，實在給我一個大力衝擊，<br />\n如一個戰士站在戰場，敵人排山倒海衝過來，我怕，切實打工血汗錢買Arkk面對大跌一定怯，<br />\n不過我冇退，我正面面對Arkk大跌，企硬，<br />\n我做到企硬。<br />\n<br />\n今日已經跌完轉升，<br />\n再一次證明Cathie正確，信Cathie正確。<br />\n<br />\n各位Arkk戰友，記住企硬！"},{"pid":"6df043dcf1dac4777dd87eaf4165a1bab281cf1c","tid":2428073,"uid":4942,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"咪撚燈啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"c26dcac822ba1a40e52c5f8de8470b9cbcfaf610","tid":2428073,"uid":21872,"like":88,"dislike":5,"score":83,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAezgCL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAezgCL.png&h=a43da1ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c75a7d1842921960fdc8525c8345187e50e2667b","tid":2428073,"uid":89184,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"入左arkg同arkk<br />\n<br />\n跟契媽買埋xone<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f4401c13e50acc04ffc0ac4bd6a68b77bff81f","tid":2428073,"uid":61886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"邪教2.0？"},{"pid":"6f496800043d3eed6f9e4172861ef3e66ff3eb5c","tid":2428073,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"契仔好榜樣<img src=\"/assets